{"tid":1358911,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"大家入嚟睇睇727對付落單警/黑社會嘅方法","createTime":"2019-07-24T04:26:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T05:52:47.000Z","uid":244889,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a82c34b7bfccdf82e6c0de089e69d7140d20470c","tid":1358911,"uid":244889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:26:57.000Z","msg":"大家見到落單既人，都掛住衝埋去打佢<br />\n而唔記得咗最緊要既一樣野<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">佢既身份</span><br />\n<br />\n最尾就導致嗰條友，係人係鬼都唔知<br />\n如果我地打佢果陣時，順便搵佢銀包<br />\n搵佢張<span style=\"color: red;\">委任證/身份證</span><br />\n<br />\n例如有個疑似警察入嚟打人<br />\n我哋就執行公民拘捕權<br />\n如果搵到佢張委任證<br />\n就提吓佢要下次<span style=\"color: red;\">要擺番出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n如果搵唔到佢張委任證<br />\n就搵身份證，告佢<span style=\"color: red;\">冒警</span><br />\n如果乜都搵唔到<br />\n就告佢<span style=\"color: red;\">非法入境</span><br />\n<br />\n至於黑社會<br />\n如果搵到佢張身分證<br />\n一定會淆曬底<br />\n著草返大陸<br />\n到時大家告咩都得<br />\n襲擊，煽惑暴動<br />\n<br />\n總之抄底佢啲資料，方便日後跟進<br />\n況且加上press既片，增加左告得入嘅機會<br />\n<br />\n大家絕對唔係攞嚟起底用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a9a1f32c1af09a07380dcd7e90931c860d15c19","tid":1358911,"uid":244889,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:27:41.000Z","msg":"仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啱啱開錯台"},{"pid":"e0d37bab23b6fd9cec1df1385156d8df58fb380d","tid":1358911,"uid":244889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:28:17.000Z","msg":"樓主英明 下次識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f2363c3e7016a877cb84d7a7438e96eb391de36","tid":1358911,"uid":18959,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:29:42.000Z","msg":"又要跟朱經緯鄭柏林之流學下野"},{"pid":"53eca8343e2eac94c31fe5f14d5e3c596c68d77f","tid":1358911,"uid":244889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9f2363c3e7016a877cb84d7a7438e96eb391de36","tid":1358911,"ui